** ER
E-01 INPUT CUSTOMER
E-02 NO DATA IN DETAIL M/F
E-03 INPUT EFFECTIVE DATE
E-04 EFFECTIVE DATE (YYMMDD) IS NOT RIGHT
E-05 INPUT EXPIRATION DATE
E-06 EXPIRATION DATE (YYMMDD) IS NOT RIGHT
E-07START DATE IS PAST DATE OF END DATE
